        %h4
          Stowaway
        %p
          Stowaway is a ruby gem that will search through the source code of 
          a web project and find all of the images, scripts and stylesheets 
          that aren't being used. To use, simply provide the path to the 
          directory you wish to search.
        %a{ :href => "http://github.com/ecavazos/stowaway" } view source
      %li
        %h4 Speks
        %p
          Speks is a simple specification framework and spec-runner for 
          %a{ :href => "http://nodejs.org/" }node.js
          code. Speks provides a set of should style prototype/extension 
          methods to make test code more readable.
        %a{ :href => "http://github.com/ecavazos/speks" } view source
          
